{
  "texts": [
    "Default settings were used for all other parameters, without any modifications.",
    "We retrieved and collected data for Chinese breast cancer cases from various online sources (www.bing.com, www.wanfang.com.cn, www.cnki.net, and www.baidu.com), including texts related to breast cancer medical care, nursing, and rehabilitation.",
    "These data sources included breast cancer textbooks, research papers, clinical guidelines, and traditional Chinese medicine knowledge.",
    "Two clinical nurses manually reviewed the materials, compared and removed duplicates, and extracted the relevant breast cancer knowledge.",
    "In cases of conflicting or inconsistent data, a third nurse provided the final adjudication."
  ]
}